      "text": "请消失吧！",
      "text_original": "消えてください！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_exskill_level_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_exskill_level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "竟敢对老师做这种事……！",
      "text_original": "先生になんてことを……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_exskill_level_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_exskill_level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "吃我这招……！",
      "text_original": "食らえ……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_exskill_level_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_exweapon_get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我这种人哪有什么资格收下这个……不，不是……既然是老师决定的。非常感谢！",
      "text_original": "私なんかがこれをいただく資格なんて……い、いえ……先生が決めたことです。ありがとうございます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_exweapon_get.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "我，我出发了！",
      "text_original": "い、いってきます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_formation_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "我，我会……尽全力的……！",
      "text_original": "さ、最善を……尽くします……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_formation_select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "合，合适吗？怎，怎么会……嘿嘿……",
      "text_original": "に、似合ってますか？そ、そんな……えへへ……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_formation_select.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "可，可能是一身难看的打扮……请，请多关照……",
      "text_original": "お、お見苦しい格好かもしれませんが……よ、よろしくお願いします……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_gachaget.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "真的……可以收下吗……？",
      "text_original": "本当に……もらっていいんですか……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_growup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "把这么珍贵的东西给我……！？该，该怎么回报您才好……！",
      "text_original": "こんなに貴重なものを私に……！？ど、どうお返しすれば……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_growup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "为了我这种人……真的，非常感谢……！",
      "text_original": "私なんかのために……本当に、ありがとうございます……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_growup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "如果有这份力量的话……把老师的敌人全部扫清也……！",
      "text_original": "この力があれば……先生の敵を全部薙ぎ払うことだって……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_growup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "请随时下令……！炸弹要多少有多少！",
      "text_original": "いつでも命令してください……！爆弾はたくさんありますので！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那，那个……有什么吩咐吗？",
      "text_original": "あ、あの……何か御用はありませんか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……诶？可以休息吗？",
      "text_original": "……え？休んでていい？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "但，但是，现在是在工作中吧……",
      "text_original": "で、ですが、今は仕事中、ですよね……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "被，被这样盯着看的话……好，好害羞……",
      "text_original": "そ、そんなに見つめられると……は、恥ずかしいです……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_lobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "尽人事……全力以赴……不择手段……",
      "text_original": "人事を尽くして……全力で……手段は問わずに……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_lobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_login_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "您，您好，老师！",
      "text_original": "こ、こんにちは、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_login_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_login_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊……穿，穿这身礼服，果，果然很怪对吧……？",
      "text_original": "あ……ど、ドレス姿、や、やっぱり変、でしょうか……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_login_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_login_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "欢，欢迎回来，老师！",
      "text_original": "お、おかえりなさい、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_login_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_login_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那个……我想让自己打起精神来，才穿了这身礼服……",
      "text_original": "ええと……気を引き締めようと思って、この格好にしたのですが……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_login_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……我喜欢杂草，并不是因为它们很美。",
      "text_original": "……雑草が好きなのは、美しいからじゃ、ないです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我喜欢杂草坚韧的部分。",
      "text_original": "私は、雑草の硬いところが好きなんです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "无论多么荒芜的土地，都能顽强地扎根生长，这种坚韧不拔的品质――",
      "text_original": "どんな荒地でも強く根を張る、粘り強さ――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那正是我的理想。",
      "text_original": "それこそが、私の理想。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不需要多么美丽。",
      "text_original": "美しくある必要はありません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不会闪闪发光也没关系。",
      "text_original": "輝かなくてもいいんです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如果能和重要的人一起度过时光……。",
      "text_original": "大切な人と、ただ過ごせるなら……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如果，能和老师一起的话……。",
      "text_original": "せ、先生と一緒にいられるのなら……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "我，就是……。",
      "text_original": "私は、それで……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_5_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_memoriallobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……喜欢，就是这样。",
      "text_original": "……好き、なんです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_memoriallobby_5_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_relationship_up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "非常感谢，非常感谢，非常感谢……！",
      "text_original": "ありがとうございます、ありがとうございます、ありがとうございます……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_relationship_up_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_relationship_up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "好漂亮……啊，这件礼服，很漂亮吧。诶，我，我吗……！？",
      "text_original": "綺麗……ああ、このドレス、綺麗ですよね。えっ、わ、私が……！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_relationship_up_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_relationship_up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我，我……可以这么幸福吗……？",
      "text_original": "わ、私……こんなに幸せでいいんでしょうか……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_relationship_up_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_relationship_up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "非常感谢。我重要的……老师……",
      "text_original": "ありがとうございます。私の大切な……先生……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_relationship_up_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_birthday_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "生，生日……我的！？诶，诶诶！？您要为我庆祝吗！？",
      "text_original": "た、誕生日……私の！？えっ、ええっ！？祝ってくださるんですか！？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_birthday_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_birthday_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "怎，怎么办才好……派对的准备什么都没做……",
      "text_original": "ど、どうしましょう……パーティーの準備なんてできてなくて……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_birthday_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_birthday_player_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "生日快乐，老师。",
      "text_original": "お誕生日おめでとうございます、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_birthday_player_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_birthday_player_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如，如果是我送的祝福也可以的话……请，请收下！",
      "text_original": "わ、私からのお祝いなんかでよければ……どうぞ、受け取ってください！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_birthday_player_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_halloween_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不给糖就捣蛋！啊，糖果——没有的话就给我子弹……！",
      "text_original": "トリックオアトリート！あ、飴――がなければ弾丸を……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_halloween_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_halloween_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……这，这样对吗？",
      "text_original": "……こ、これで合ってますか？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_halloween_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_newyear",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐……那个……是一年的开始哦……？和我这样的人一起度过真的好吗……？",
      "text_original": "明けましておめでとうございます……。あの……一年の始まりですよ……？私なんかと過ごしていて本当にいいんですか……？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_newyear.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_xmas_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "圣诞快乐……！",
      "text_original": "メリークリスマス、です……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_xmas_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_season_xmas_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如果老师希望的话……我去把圣诞老人抓来！",
      "text_original": "先生がご希望でしたら……サンタを捕獲してきます！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_season_xmas_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_defeat_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "全，全都，是我的错。很抱歉……！",
      "text_original": "ぜ、ぜんぶ、私のせいです。申し訳ありません……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_defeat_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_defeat_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "请，请把我丢掉吧……！",
      "text_original": "もう、捨てて下さい……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_defeat_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_in_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "只要和老师在一起，无论去哪里……！",
      "text_original": "先生と一緒なら、どこへでも……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_in_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_in_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "所有人……都消灭掉……！",
      "text_original": "全員……潰します……！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_victory_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "果，果然老师好厉害！",
      "text_original": "や、やっぱり先生はすごいです！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_victory_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch0247_tactic_victory_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "是！垃圾已经扔进垃圾桶了！",
      "text_original": "はい！ゴミはゴミ箱にぶち込みました！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BC%8A%E8%8D%89%20%E9%81%A5%E9%A6%99/%E7%A4%BC%E6%9C%8D/jp/ch0247_tactic_victory_2.ogg"
    },
